Package: cassandra-tools-wmf
Architecture: all
Depends: python-yaml (>= 3.11), ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Description: add-ons to make Wikimedia Cassandra operations easier
 Contains the following:
 .
   - c-ls: lists local Cassandra instance names
   - c-foreach-nt: wrapper for nodetool; Sequentially executes nodetool for
     each local Cassandra instance.
   - c-foreach-restart: iteratively restart all instances
   - c-cqlsh: given an instance name, connects to Cassandra using cqlsh,
     (utilizing any configuration in /etc/cassandra-{instance}/cqlshrc)
   - uyaml: helper for reading yaml files from shell
